          <p>‡πÄ‡∏á‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà: {parseFloat(result.newPrincipal).toLocaleString()} ‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏ó</p>
